code: @Override public void write(int b) throws IOException {     out.writeByte((byte) b). }
@Override public void write(byte[] b) throws IOException {     out.writeBytes(b, b.length). }
@Override public void write(byte[] b, int off, int len) throws IOException {     out.writeBytes(b, off, len). }
@Override public void close() throws IOException {     out.close(). }
